snippet.title: Amber Heard stuns in glamorous gown on red carpet at Cannes
snippet.description:
Cannes Fim Festival draws stars from around the world, including some of Hollywood's elite.   And Amber Heard and Alessandra Ambrosio led the model glamour as they arrived in style at the premiere of Les Miserable during the 71st annual Cannes Film Festival on Wednesday night.  Amber stunned in a dazzling gown, while Alessandra looked fiery in a bold red number as they stepped out on the red carpet.
